BarcodeScannerStub - Class in com.contentbeach.barcode.scanner.stub
Utilizes the KeyboardSendInputHelper to end keyboard events to a Windows-based application window.

C

com.contentbeach.barcode.scanner.stub - package com.contentbeach.barcode.scanner.stub
Contains a barcode scanner stub class (BarcodeScannerStub) that uses the KeyboardSendInputHelper to send keyboard events to a Windows-based application window (the window must be open and not minimized).
com.contentbeach.jna.input.keyboard - package com.contentbeach.jna.input.keyboard
Provides the classes that utilize JNA to send keyboard events to applications running on a Windows platform.
